omote early sexual activity and it doesn&rsquo;t promote any particular sexual orientation.</p>\n\n<p>Some elements of sex and relationship education are mandatory - these are part of the national curriculum for science. Parents can withdraw their children from all other parts of sex and relationship education if they want.</p>\n\n<h2>Religious education</h2>\n\n<p>Schools also have to teach religious education but parents can withdraw their children for all or part of the lessons. Local councils are responsible for deciding on a syllabus.</p>\n\n"}]},"tags":[{"title":"School life","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/education%2Fschool-life.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Help with school costs, the curriculum and school attendance","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=education%2Fschool-life","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/education/school-life"},"parent":{"title":"Education and learning","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/education.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Get help if you&#39;re at school, planning to go on to further or higher education, looking for training or interested in a student or career development loan.","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=education","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/education"},"parent":null}}],"related":[{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/school-term-holiday-dates.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/school-term-holiday-dates","title":"School term and holiday dates","format":"local_transaction","updated_at":"2012-10-22T15:17:29+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/types-of-school.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/types-of-school","title":"Types of school ","format":"guide","updated_at":"2012-10-22T15:25:56+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/home-schooling-information-council.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/home-schooling-information-council","ti